{"tid":2177562,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"傻閪福X中學(小西灣）訓導主任EQ真係有問題","createTime":"2020-08-27T21:15:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T03:51:33.000Z","uid":365136,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"74b4f4e6981a5d49b498bc86a7999c6bf0e14462","tid":2177562,"uid":365136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T21:15:18.000Z","msg":"是咁的，本人已經離開校園，但看到條傻閪日日喺度自把自為，欺凌弱小同學，真係睇唔過眼。<br />\n首先，2014年開學前的預備班，條傻閪講到違例泊車好似冇問題咁，罰錢了事就算。但係你知唔知咁樣係好影響到人例如其他道路使用者。就係你呢啲冚家剷搞到咁多交通意外同塞車問題。一旦你條冚家剷阻住架救護車救人，病人死撚咗，咁你又會點解決呢。呢啲咪叫自私囉,有車位就唔泊，慳果幾十蚊，真市儈。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其次，本人在中四的時候，在走廊無意聽到訓導主任鬧緊個學生，咁我又聽到條傻閪講[打我啦 ！］等類似的字句。其實你呢啲係咩訓導，叫返個同學仔打你？正常人難以明白。黑社會？黑警？咁你同啲黑社會真係冇分別囉。我真心唔信有啲咁嘅訓導理論。你讀咁撚多書同啲黑社會冇分別，真係浪費社會啲資源，你唔撚死都冇撚用。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再者，本人在中六的時候帶黑色口罩返學，但係就係俾你條傻閪截住咗，要求我除下。你係乜撚嘢身份姐，城管？公安？學校有乜撚嘢校規唔俾學生戴口罩？如果學校有撚規例嘅話，咁我都冇計。咁事實上係冇吖嘛，你條撚樣仲要聲大夾惡要我除下，仲要記校服儀容不整，你係咪癡Q左線？戴口罩就係校服儀容不整，你老母冚家剷啦咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nAs a result, 你呢啲人唔死都冇撚用㗎啦，希望你快啲俾雷劈死，睇你仲咁健康龍精虎猛咁，幾時先穿腸破肚，七孔流血，橫屍街頭，你搵埋咁多冤枉錢，成日講大話，遲早一定死無葬身之地。引用孔子的一句［<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">汝安則為之</span></span>］和 大時代丁蟹都講［<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">人善人欺天不欺 人惡人怕天不怕］</span></span>，希望你快啲比天收, <span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">最後仲有佢情緒失控嘅片段</span></span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hEJBcrC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhEJBcrC.jpg&h=5d7f69ee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HMNZadi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHMNZadi.jpg&h=6eb249f2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qu8UJyi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqu8UJyi.jpg&h=84f54197&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1hf4mjZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1hf4mjZ.png&h=3c648ab5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4H9s3yk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4H9s3yk.jpg&h=bc4ff58e&s={SIZE}\" />[url][url]<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9SeaL9aOkOw[/urI]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9SeaL9aOkOw%5B%2FurI%5D&d=Bx5vHrS2V4FMjGMjdccONirXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=d6518909\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9SeaL9aOkOw[/urI]</a>"},{"pid":"e1f10e94d582df8fff77615690b8bb041f6ce867","tid":2177562,"uid":365136,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T21:16:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9SeaL9aOkOw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9SeaL9aOkOw&d=Bx5vHrS2V4FMjGMjdccONirXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=27615e20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9SeaL9aOkOw</a>"},{"pid":"577dfc63716ea9c97638dd57acc13543c8963328","tid":2177562,"uid":365136,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T21:44:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hk4MzQ2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHk4MzQ2.png&h=faa07d0b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e0b549969f806673872ed04961810385b6f07cd7","tid":2177562,"uid":365136,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T16:22:15